org.rx.functions
Class Functions

java.lang.Object
  org.rx.functions.Functions

public class Functions
extends java.lang.Object

Allows execution of functions from multiple different languages.

Language support is provided via implementations of FunctionLanguageAdaptor.

This class will dynamically look for known language adaptors on the classpath at startup or new ones can be registered using Functions.registerLanguageAdaptor(Class, FunctionLanguageAdaptor).
